templates.body:
Dear {BROKER_NAME},

I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to express our interest in the {DEAL_NAME} opportunity that you are representing.

{COMPANY_NAME} is an active acquirer in the {INDUSTRY} space, and based on our preliminary review, this opportunity appears to align well with our investment criteria.

We would appreciate the opportunity to learn more about this business. Could we schedule a brief call this week to discuss the opportunity in more detail?

Key areas of interest:
- Business overview and history
- Financial performance summary
- Growth opportunities
- Reason for sale

I look forward to speaking with you soon.

Best regards,
{USER_NAME}
{USER_TITLE}
{COMPANY_NAME}
{USER_PHONE}
{USER_EMAIL}

Dear {SELLER_NAME},

I wanted to provide you with a weekly update on our due diligence progress for {DEAL_NAME}.

Completed this week:
- {COMPLETED_ITEM_1}
- {COMPLETED_ITEM_2}
- {COMPLETED_ITEM_3}

In progress:
- {IN_PROGRESS_1}
- {IN_PROGRESS_2}

Upcoming:
- {UPCOMING_1}
- {UPCOMING_2}

Outstanding items needed:
- {NEEDED_1}
- {NEEDED_2}

We remain on track for our target closing date of {CLOSING_DATE}. The process is going smoothly, and we appreciate your team's responsiveness.

Please let me know if you have any questions or concerns.

Best regards,
{USER_NAME}

Dear {SELLER_NAME},

We are pleased to submit the attached Letter of Intent to acquire {DEAL_NAME}.

Key terms of our proposal:
- Purchase Price: ${PURCHASE_PRICE}
- Structure: {DEAL_STRUCTURE}
- Closing Timeline: {TIMELINE}
- Due Diligence Period: {DD_PERIOD}
- Exclusivity Period: {EXCLUSIVITY}

This offer reflects our strong interest in {DEAL_NAME} and our commitment to completing this transaction. We believe our proposal provides excellent value while ensuring a smooth transition for all stakeholders.

We are prepared to move quickly and have the necessary resources in place to complete this transaction.

I would welcome the opportunity to discuss this proposal with you. Please let me know your availability for a call this week.

We look forward to your response.

Sincerely,
{USER_NAME}
{USER_TITLE}
{COMPANY_NAME}

Dear {RECIPIENT_NAME},

I am thrilled to announce that {BUYER_COMPANY} has completed the acquisition of {SELLER_COMPANY}, effective {CLOSING_DATE}.

This acquisition represents an important milestone in our growth strategy and strengthens our position in the {INDUSTRY} market. {SELLER_COMPANY}'s {KEY_STRENGTH} perfectly complements our existing capabilities.

Key highlights:
- {HIGHLIGHT_1}
- {HIGHLIGHT_2}
- {HIGHLIGHT_3}

For customers: You will continue to receive the same excellent products/services, now with additional resources and support.

For employees: We are excited to welcome the {SELLER_COMPANY} team and look forward to growing together.

We will be sharing more details about our integration plans in the coming weeks. In the meantime, please feel free to reach out with any questions.

Best regards,
{USER_NAME}
{USER_TITLE}
{BUYER_COMPANY}

